      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neffeet juhfas Teetas\nLeetas ſchurp/ ſakka tas KUNgas:\nAtneffeet/ ar ko juhs ſawas Leetas\nwarrat parahdiht/ ſakka tas\nJehkaba Rehninſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lai tee ſtahſta/ un mums bija neweens/\nſluddina tahs Leetas/ kas wehl ſcheein/ bet newa nekahds Pa-\nnotiks. Stabſtajt tahs pirmas dohma-Dewejs/ ka es tohs war-\nLeetas / kas bijuschas irr / ka retu waizaht/ un tee man at-\nmehs tahs muhſn Sirdi nem-\nman/ un to Gallu no ta fin-\nnam. Neb lerzeet mums nahka-\nmas Leetas klaufiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Stabſtajt tahs Leetas/\nkas wehl pakkat buhs/ ka mehs\natsibſtam juhs Deewus effam.\nUn darrajt labba/ darrajt arri-\ndsan tanna/ tad mehs brihniti-\nnees/ un redſefim kohpa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Raugi/ juhs effat masaki\nnefa neneeka/ un juhsu Darbs\nirr kannaks neka Nhdſe/ tas irr\npar Negantibu / kas juhs is-\nwehlehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es usmohdinaju weenu\nno Seemeta Puſſes/ un wiꞥſch\nnahks no Saules Uslehkschanas/\ntas fluddinahs mannu Wahr-\ndu/ wiꞥſch ees pahr teem Wald-\nnekeem ta pahr Dubkeem/ un\nka weens Pohdneeks to Mahlu\nmin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas warr ko ſtabſtibt no\nEſahkuma/ ka mehs to finnam?\nneb no pagahjuſcheim Latkeem?\ntad fazziftin mehs: Wiꞥſch irr\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es tas pirmajs (fakku)\nus Zianu: Redſi / teju tas irr/\nun us Jeruſalemi: Es dohchu\nweenu preezigu Sluddinataju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es usrandsiju/ tad ne\nirr patt ſtarp\nſcheein/ bet newa nekahds Pa-\ndohma-Dewejs/ ka es tohs war-\nretu waizaht/ un tee man at-\nbildetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redſi / tee irr wiſsnotuk\nNefeetiba/ winno Darbi irr ne-\nleeschi/ winnu leetas Bildes irr\nWehſch un neleetiga Leeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ne weens irr/ kas\nto ſtabſta / ir netweens/ kas ko\nlabbu leek dsirdeht/ ir netweens/\nkas jubahs Wahrdus klanta.\n"
    }
  ],
